description:
Embrace the electric power of the Rimac Concept_One and the Raesr Tachyon Speed and unleash these silent speed machines onto the Asphalt 9: Legends streets.

This pack contains:
• Blueprints to unlock the Rimac Concept_One
• Blueprints to unlock the Raesr Tachyon Speed
• 1,500,000 Credits
• 1,500 Tokens
name: Asphalt 9: Legends Electric Power Racing Pack
